    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device where model influence is Medium and experimental confirmation is available. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 across all five COU operating points at the chosen configuration settings (y+ ≈ 3.8, C_th = 1.8 × 10⁻⁵, k-ω SST with C_μ = 0.09). The credibility assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
